{"tid":1944372,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性分析] 其實恆指24000點樓下 買2800根本無得輸","createTime":"2020-03-26T10:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T10:53:51.000Z","uid":73241,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01f9c7ad18886d4f0366265274bfce1973e64efa","tid":1944372,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"今日2020年3月26日記錄：<br />\n盈富基金（2800）收市價$23.60<br />\n無人知宜家恆指見底未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但可能性只有兩個<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 21139.26已見底</span></strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能10年、20年<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至永遠都唔再見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁既情況下 現價買2800<br />\n完全係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無撚得輸</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為等佢升到咁上下 收息又得 長揸又得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任君選揀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>2. 21139.26未見底</ins></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果現價買入 最多都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正股驚閪</span></strong></span><br />\n長線黎講 恆指點都會再升上去<br />\n現價就係低位<br />\n再講啦 如果跌穿二萬一<br />\n新低可能都係萬八左右<br />\n其實現價買 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><strong><ins>最盡都係坐25%</ins></strong></em></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長線都係有息收 又可能半年就升番上黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以</span></strong></span><br />\n與其等一個最低最低位先入市<br />\n或者一個唔知會唔會出現